===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|cicen|ċicen|lang=ang|sc=Latinx}}, {{term|cycen||chicken|lang=ang}}, diminuitive of {{term|coc|lang=ang}}, {{term|cocc||cock, rooster|lang=ang}}. Cognate with {{etyl|nl|-}} {{term|kuiken|lang=nl}}, {{term|kicken||chick, chicken|lang=nl}}, {{etyl|nds|-}} {{term|küken||chicken|lang=nds}}, {{etyl|de|-}} {{term|Küken||chick|lang=de}}, {{etyl|de|-}} dialectal {{term|Küchlein||chicken|lang=de}}. More at [[cock]], [[-en#Etymology_5|-en]].

